  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 박스 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-464501a5-37bf-4a1f-9ccb-5e43ab64892a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">단상자의 견적</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">단상자의 견적은 패키지 박스 중에 일단 가장 저렴합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0420fc2-f91d-44ac-ad80-bad425b1a603\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9365d6b8-5072-4241-a463-464ad8d4df08\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35368eb7-3363-4581-947d-b194c8ea3683\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ae938ec-a989-483f-8bfc-0ebb025528ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 저렴한 이유는 일단 종이가 한 종류로만 제작되기 때문입니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dc8953db-9285-47e5-8326-9c2c4c4bc4b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>한 종류의 종이로만 만드는 것이 단상자입니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c733cfd-69ed-4c47-877a-4ba855c1c8e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 이 때문에 단상자는 보통 300g 이상의 두꺼운 종이로 제작이 됩니다. 300g의 종이는 명함으로 따지면 가장 두꺼운 종이 정도라고 생각하시면 됩니다. 가장 많이 사용하는 종이는 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e989f86f-1358-4598-9c60-3335391a8f0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25928195-3cef-41bc-9a90-f406c288f7b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c59a263-1ffa-4d9f-965d-06b3925dd177\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a36ee5f4-48f4-4468-bfc9-580acaeecabd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>마닐라지 (마분지)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-fcf2d2a6-e0b1-4018-9542-5314a4e3273a\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8952f96c-0b8f-4944-a337-27d15d25cec1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b93a60b4-c70f-4b5e-8bb8-031d038f9537\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83ffea77-c5a6-4fc8-8a20-8ad50bbbd73f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">마닐라는 박스 종이 중에 가장 저렴한 종이입니다. 위 이미지처럼 뒷면에는 인쇄가 불가능할 정도로 거친 회색입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-709759c8-e7e4-4dfb-8f67-50802b9108f7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-524feea5-af70-48d0-b96f-c91ff00532d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22a8f833-9daa-4602-af28-961400843a55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c40f075b-b25d-43d2-a191-b68c67c705e4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">평량은 300g ~ 500g까지 다양합니다. 주로 단가가 중요한 포장재로 사용되고 차, 티, 식료품 포장박스로 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3abe9e03-5444-433e-a64a-46def0f44cf7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-680383fb-d12f-4f40-bea2-c61dcd5e172e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-04c485a9-1491-417a-a75e-dc50de30238d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d68f9c79-7ff4-493f-b8d4-a12f2bdf2576\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db7170d6-289a-475f-a121-c72dff5fda9a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f183add-b702-4807-aea4-f87b739a1049\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아이보리지 (IV)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-6a9b8dbe-5731-43e6-a538-714c460303b1\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3188b2a9-4c3c-4570-b512-014b06c12e27\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45d1882a-d9ff-4725-b0ce-a9f6caa300e2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4e478ea-9e2e-43c4-b7a1-054731b432e6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아이보리지는 가장 많이 사용되는 패키지 종이입니다. 양면 인쇄가 가능할 뿐 아니라 내구성이나 인쇄 발색력이 뛰어나 가장 사랑받는 종이입니다. 로열 아이보리는 미색이 나면서 더 뛰어난 발색력을 자랑합니다. BV / BW처럼 브랜드에 따라 편면과 양면으로 구별됩니다. 패키지는 양면인쇄가 거의 없으므로 단면 아이보리도 많이 사용됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03cbad9d-4670-4d29-a55c-31448277f03b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2794d65-2ac2-4db2-8312-b634f15e3dbf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f044e68f-50b0-4622-94b9-b290da03b982\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff1079d8-7bf2-4350-81c3-b9866c70e657\" style=\"color:#555555;\">평량은 300g ~ 450g까지 다양합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3849d58c-eee0-4b47-af0b-6d6f1b461426\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d087af3f-7ee7-4ea4-87b6-386f6630b13c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d5fa1010-cbeb-4304-b19b-f10d5fd390ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6c91e5d7-d4e4-40b4-9ef7-380628749752\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1767b99-019f-4b5c-b9dd-a5418e2d0675\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4a2f39b9-00bb-4b4e-b6ff-4aa93f2d0e9b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>CCP (코팅액)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-e7fc5ae1-06ec-479c-8ff8-1a416f3fb34e\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02623896-39e2-41ee-a43e-30b6a33c28bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3a41a8c-91d7-4315-905c-350fd4637221\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0124ef49-0989-4dce-908f-c9729c3523d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">CCP지는 코팅이 기본으로 처리된 종입니다. 유광으로 반짝이는 유광택 코팅액이 미세하게 도포되어 있어서 코팅처리를 원하는 반짝이는 포장재로 사랑받고 있습니다. 매끄러우면서 유광 코팅액이 도포되어 매끈한 표면을 선호하는 고객님이 가장 많이 선택하는 종이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-03119e50-1c57-48fb-98ae-54bfbc51353e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-530cf31f-0ba0-4ce2-a25d-c6197fca42bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b031eac-1eca-4080-885e-5b19724dcdf3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cde1a536-e6fc-4565-b235-a8e9507e2f79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">평량은 300g ~ 400g까지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8837c9af-dfc6-40a3-a949-e1bb8758a03c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-567778d7-72ab-41c1-8eea-057dbe3997a6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ce91a4b-19a4-451b-9b4e-b81966569340\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8c1e1d17-9b6a-47c1-ae5d-7dded0115e7e\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>견적의 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac45b52b-aad7-4c95-a306-7cf5a06c2d7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fcbe3cb6-b554-463f-9077-09b79596011f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적은 다음과 같이 구성됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96ffc2f9-0511-4215-826a-7b260567f6ba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb8bd6de-acc3-49ba-b6d1-1441e9603b1e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51c73ddc-653e-4ee3-9f76-a195d47d89b2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5c8b7586-6bec-41d4-a91d-955cba52698d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a24beaea-e7aa-4ae8-9b62-95de57184e6c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae40e94b-382d-46bc-84a9-26802cf0a232\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자이기 때문에 하나의 종이비가 계산됩니다. 이 종이 비용은 전개도의 사이즈에 따라 결정됩니다. 단상자의 전개도가 A4에 들어가는 사이즈라면 A4 기준으로 종이 비용이 계산됩니다. A4는 국 8절입니다. 그러므로 기본 종이비는 4,000개 기준으로 모든 것이 계산됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9fcc997c-b4c5-417b-8ad9-bc351b1a1e60\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b1e6fa7-7d0e-4e60-a599-d29d7300bdb7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4811794f-05e5-47e0-8b30-002d51c2fe73\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d73c7dd-2c08-49ba-8481-88813022942a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 로열 아아보리 400g 이 1R에 200,000원이라면 단상자 4,000장의 종이 비용은 200,000 +  여분으로 견적이 도출될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbbdca10-5531-4f5b-9f54-45edc62e5577\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29eb524f-b92f-4c12-aaba-2f9f32d2b84e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c0804eb-9b9d-48f4-9ff3-69f7e3895ff8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4c0f9a22-0611-462d-abd8-4ca79788e335\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>출력비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f034e1b1-3f5f-4489-8d3a-b310f437feea\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16677c6a-7f78-4983-be3f-279671a43232\" style=\"color:#555555;\">출력비용은 인쇄 도수와 관계가 있습니다. CMYK로 제작이 된다면 CTP는 인쇄 절수에 따라 4도 비용이 청구될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-13ed1377-f397-4a83-8ee4-b84718d0ef7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8463ffe5-c64d-406f-8046-e0ebaacb373c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-861abfa4-e20b-4ae4-9e57-9efd57c0c55a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2f2d2180-4f58-446b-bb72-1feb1ea6981a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통상의 경우 국전 CTP 비용은 조달청 단가 기준으로 제작됩니다. 조달청 단가표는 다음 파일을 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3ff531f-0544-4841-bce8-fdf8a96e028f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-284015ca-762e-4d5b-8462-d190decefe28\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-file se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d412d2ba-e7ac-4d45-b91e-d6ae3f2f5bfc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-file se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-file\">\n<span class=\"se-file-icon\"><strong class=\"se-blind\">첨부파일</strong></span>\n<div class=\"se-file-name-container\">\n<span class=\"se-file-name\">KISA 2024년 인쇄 단가표</span><span class=\"se-file-extension\">.pdf</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"se-file-save-button __se_link\" data-linktype=\"file\" href=\"https://download.blog.naver.com/open/b025ac1962553c81a3472a1329ccb6cd6e3e59/EFsQaLdMxbvO9dJYLuoSggWaFwbSq-dpeF8XKG00xEFxTtTRU3oi5fe3DYVghi0mriSOCQHe4lg-wR9SORKFdEJeC4RmQ5ELL4Ws_w/KISA%202024%EB%85%84%20%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84%20%EB%8B%A8%EA%B0%80%ED%91%9C.pdf\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">파일 다운로드</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a148e73-3417-4979-a5aa-9a4514ac96e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28cbfcf7-6bfd-47ce-a179-98f474b54b41\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f4721a4-fd57-48fe-93de-027fafb7f6e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별색은 별색출력비가 따로 청구됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e520f295-c028-4599-b505-27c4a0e3760a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-916fb6e6-2ca9-4a9a-a445-4240f430a424\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6795da0c-9246-4ba9-ac70-b80eb90b5c53\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f66fa4bd-9bb4-4400-9a5a-a2355a94f09f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ec7e3c77-e47a-4468-bcec-c489e5d84f8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c09e714d-95a5-42f1-9ccd-d6d8ced19b3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄비는 통수 또는 R 수 단위로 계산됩니다. R 수는 기본 인쇄비 단가이므로 A4에 한 개의 전개도가 들어간다면 4,000개까지는 기본 인쇄비가 책정된다는 뜻입니다. 모든 계산이 통수 단위로 계산되기 때문에 4,000개를 제작하나 1,000개를 제작하나 종이비 차이밖에 발생하지 않을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-74d94294-c5fd-4490-81de-f25bcf7d8364\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-abb43924-a95e-4b68-a213-ea366ff364a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88295adc-8a6d-4a33-9cbb-8a4961c4fb17\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e407b2a-aacd-4cfb-b3f6-06a6627ca771\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">고객님과 통화 시에 가장 설명이 길게 필요한 부분이 기본 수량에 대한 것입니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8bf98a6c-6c92-4856-93f8-ab5a13457305\" style=\"color:#555555;\">장폭고 전개도 사이즈에 따라 절수를 계산하여 기본 수량을 알려드립니다. 인쇄비 뿐 아니라 코팅, 접착, 목형도 다 기본 수량에 의해 계산됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08a7018c-bcab-4085-acca-1c9fa13a7ddf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0755aec4-f158-464d-aa7b-6a7f03d7801f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33fa494b-488b-490d-be94-46e806807547\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-709d6c75-ef39-4aa7-a363-a3a849ca13ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c65f96ca-7892-4535-93a5-b30013ca329e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ef3bfa0-4629-4ea7-b5fb-6b2beb3ad888\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정비용은 코팅, 목형, 도무송(톰슨), 접착 등이 발생됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77298e8b-d0e9-4f49-bd74-462b81c674a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d1f3acf-ca2f-4d77-a94d-3915546d69b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e9d21868-ec13-443f-a4cc-44fd8e253663\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbdebf8f-da3f-4f85-8f6b-5e96dc5d925d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코팅도 기본 절수에 따른 통수로 계산됩니다. 1연에 얼마 이런 식으로 계산됩니다. 이런 이유로 3,000개나 4,000개가 비슷하게 견적이 청구될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9219a971-f58f-46d1-8f02-ae071fde6041\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e5e6a09-7bf5-4331-91f3-ca1a2022b8b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-285ad026-60d8-45a1-ae14-08d2d31d630a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2c5c8b4-829c-4e8a-bca2-075a8b1b3563\" style=\"color:#555555;\">목형은 초기에 제작되고 재발주시에는 목형 비용이 빠질 수 있습니다. 대부분의 패키지 업체는 목형비를 추가 주문 시에는 DC 해 드립니다. 만약에 빼주지 않으면 요구하셔도 됩니다. 또한 견적 시 목형비를 별도로 청구하여 재주문시 할인이라고 견적하는 회사도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2873dca-772a-4545-81bf-f667aafa7723\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:790px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b445477-3e85-4bfc-9fa7-a4757f5d9a4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92e95c43-6163-42ee-8f1f-e39bebfc1138\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa953a60-9440-4b9a-bfbe-030abe33ca2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">접착의 경우는 소량은 수작업으로 진행되어 더 비싸질 수 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cdc2742a-51dd-4fc6-8d6e-4e84025f8ed6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f58f8a8-75ab-4154-b155-bf8c3f929b92\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-477c0646-ff4d-4aaf-b241-25065d21be84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f2d77f6-4eb6-4752-9795-1b519f03b480\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적서는 다음처럼 청구됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5834619e-795f-4ed4-bd20-6a47f0c662a4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:616px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899195451/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a659d247-0280-4ce5-a267-08a50de80a41\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d979d5b3-36d6-46c5-879f-01187a266c47\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ef2066c7-47ca-4c2c-a486-1c7fc5c0003e\" style=\"\">디지털 소량의 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b3b149c-d763-4351-ab9d-1bc405e89770\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98e968d4-84f6-4e4b-8964-d3b3e7ced8ad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8444c07a-6b4b-4a5e-9f6c-d8f6c2c7f351\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적은 디지털의 경우는 완전히 다릅니다. 수량이 200개 미만의 경우가 대부분이고 종이도 디지털 전용지로 달라집니다. 인쇄도 디지털은 별색으로 진행되지 않고 사이즈에 대한 제약이 가장 큽니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ffcee50e-84c4-47fd-8359-b3ed4ff0f26b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8c19a34-c0b6-41fa-b956-ae027a2406d6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-767d0c56-3709-442c-8561-55d5e7d4d681\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-40e2d6ff-dd28-4253-91b0-fec87b15ed7a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 소량 박스</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d06fcb54-f14f-42b1-aff6-f30b9c153e5e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d66e3284-466e-4b61-a25b-ddea5ab9facb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 : 디지털 전용지 (별도 문의)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b506141-e515-41bc-853c-d15829078e23\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f33d37df-6a4f-44bc-b877-9a0f266b8437\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈 : A3 이내</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8329bcfa-c449-4baa-a2f7-419e4369ba64\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-42eaf4c6-1521-492c-a402-edf7fd01b35e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 : CMYK 4도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f04842fd-7c6f-4ec3-9c50-7090289b654e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a0595a12-c197-4ef2-baee-7d139f04820d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코팅 : 무광/유광 라미네이팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa72a154-61db-447c-9adf-bb7991e825bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a65f8230-88e1-4d22-9ceb-755f63829c3e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">커팅 : 디지털 커팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83cccd6e-a6a9-4348-afc7-55451aed2856\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-436d8923-c4c0-444b-9155-c6b42291a29e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">접착 : 양면테이프나 글루건 수작업</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-644b49e2-432b-4810-aebb-f93c7f17a1df\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d4ae0fad-06b7-4594-8ba7-e7dba925e490\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량 : 200개 미만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b095f90a-5062-4d01-a78b-5cf085e04f9a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96891aac-ea77-4852-afd6-9d9e698384c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3c6756da-c7f3-4404-85f6-30b98a6f3b3d\" style=\"\">주문방법</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02e16e8f-251b-4baf-a1b6-e80bd812663b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22d67dd9-b9f8-43aa-8331-d20b8b2a0733\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7fdc752b-6f2c-4cdf-870c-07c2fb83410a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 들어가는 제품을 알려주세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a01676a-34bd-475b-afb4-fe0a9e7e9a1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f9c01eca-c8b4-4d27-8693-62e273080666\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품을 알아야 무게나 종이 등을 추천해 드릴 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86e9db37-1ed5-49b5-ad1c-59f34057c3c7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2baf89ac-70f4-436d-b8c5-b7713bb60a26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-edd46512-9d57-4b44-96f6-5732e4140eb8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-de25fb1b-5322-4538-b139-1630ce541d53\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 장폭고 사이즈와 형태</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-900ecc8b-14ba-4c21-bab5-d0b5ca9fc302\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55531f76-7d39-4320-b2ef-ca70ba853d96\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 중요한 사이즈를 알려주셔야 합니다. 이 사이즈를 알려주면서 형태를 말씀 주시면 칼선을 보내드립니다. 칼선에 의해 디자인 작업을 하시고 견적을 검토하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d4d56560-13ae-4043-8af8-08dbb3e17b9a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9bc36a3c-737c-48a2-88ce-dd2fe0aa1f76\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f8d6bfc-ba67-4ef5-9b14-8a54a35c36fa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ed6f4b2-c987-4a51-9bd5-4ebf1a0b74ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 견적서, 디자인 파일 컨펌</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3bdda35b-40e2-4664-acb2-dab886fbd1f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9e1be71c-f0d3-4f20-93ef-111077018437\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적서와 디자인 파일은 컨펌하면 진행을 시작합니다. 견적서를 검토하실 때는 금액뿐 아니라 납기 생산 방법 등등을 꼼꼼히 검토하시기 바랍니다. 저희와 거래를 하지 않더라도 납기는 반드시 체크하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-65e284be-8538-4d65-8a6f-93fea9e34d6d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90aeda55-705f-4849-9355-1a182fdfc194\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-74f84fab-2f18-49ac-b755-f47b9c6a5690\" style=\"\">납기</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78dc68c9-4a6d-404a-bb88-fb714d557743\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e1994596-fa4e-41cf-8a9e-1a5abd086717\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9508308-8026-403e-a070-08681c41bb5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플용 1 ~ 5개 : 1일 ~ 2일 택배 발송 기본</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57e895d2-fde1-46dc-899b-e5d1d6ca053d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4678d971-f0f1-40d4-ba3b-79a5e627166c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 생산 : 100개 미만은 2일 ~ 4일</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8f647f0-8084-4cd5-b6c2-44fb4ab732bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2499c9aa-6031-49f6-afd3-aec922bd208a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 대량 생산 : 200개까지는 3일 ~ 5일 사이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9db95c71-1e8f-47d8-93ba-cab5dd1eb2a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aad8dd6b-bfc2-4d1f-adb2-03e21d0aeb22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1154922c-bba6-44eb-be12-eb149e5a058b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1320001-f38f-4a6c-b1ac-a55434656efa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">납기는 반드시 상의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77377009-7503-4065-938d-3de28e8663ac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c35cf3ee-a2a8-4e3f-b422-545df6fd79fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223899195451#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
